node.text:
Good morning! 😍 This lakefront home is located at 6020 Le Lac Road in Boca Raton, Florida and is situated on 6.7 acres of land. 

It was built in 2014 and features approximately 11,281 square feet of living space with 8 bedrooms, 9 full and 1 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, 2-story great room, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen, breakfast/family room with wet bar, home office, gym, garage and more.

Outdoor features include a loggia with kitchen/BBQ, patio, boat dock and a resort-style swimming pool complete with spa, rock waterfall, lazy river and 2 water slides. The pool alone cost $2.5 million to build and was inspired by Atlantis Paradise Island in the Bahamas.

🌍 6020 Le Lac Road, Boca Raton, Florida 🏠 11,281 Square Feet 🛏 8 Bedrooms 🛁 10 Bathrooms 💰 Sold for $5,500,000

node.text:
Good morning! 😍 This stunning home, dubbed “Maison De Reve”, is located in Woodland Hills, Utah. It was designed/built by @buildwithdavies with interior design by @marissapopedesign 

It features nearly 20,000 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 13 bathrooms, foyer with staircase, formal living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, built-in breakfast nook, conservatory, office, craft room, man cave, playroom, game room with wet bar, home theater, indoor basketball court, 4-car main level garage, subterranean showroom garage and much more. 

Outdoor features include a motor court, terraces/patios and a pool.

Photography by @jaredmedley

Good afternoon! 😍 This newly built French style stone home is located at 18 Close Road in Greenwich, Connecticut and is situated on 27 acres of land.

It features approximately 17,198 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 8 full and 2 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer, multiple staircases, elevator, formal living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, office, game room, gym, indoor swimming pool, 4-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a motor court, balconies/patios, fireplace, tennis court with pavilion, gazebo, boathouse and a dock.

🌍 18 Close Road, Greenwich, Connecticut 🏠 17,198 Square Feet 🛏 6 Bedrooms 🛁 10 Bathrooms 💰 $40,000,000

node.text:
Goodnight! 😍 This shingle style home is located at 889 S Colfax Avenue in Elmhurst, Illinois and is situated on over half an acre of land.

It was built in 2016 and features approximately 11,108 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 7 full and 2 half bathrooms, foyer with staircase, formal living room, dining room, gourmet kitchen, family room, sunroom, office, billiards room/lounge with wet bar, home theater, gym, indoor basketball court, 4-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a covered front porch, balcony, covered patio with fireplace, kitchen/BBQ with pizza oven, fire pit and a putting green.

🌍 889 S Colfax Avenue, Elmhurst, Illinois 🏠 11,108 Square Feet 🛏 7 Bedrooms 🛁 9 Bathrooms 💰 $3,995,000

node.text:
Good morning! 😍 This newly built traditional style home is located at 614 Bermuda Isle Street on Daniel Island in Charleston, South Carolina and is situated on 2/3 of an acre of land.

It features approximately 15,000 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 7 full and 1 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with double staircase, elevator, living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen with double islands, office, rec room, golf simulator, home theater, wine cellar, two 3-car garages with 4 Tesla charging stations and more.

Outdoor features include a motor court, porches & patios, fireplace and a swimming pool with spa.

Photography by @nickcannphoto
@nickcann_ 

🌍 614 Bermuda Isle Street, Daniel Island, South Carolina 🏠 15,000 Square Feet 🛏 6 Bedrooms 🛁 8 Bathrooms 💰 $6,925,000

Good morning! 😍 This stucco & brick home is located at 263 Mount Laurel Road in Mount Laurel, New Jersey and is situated on nearly 3 acres of land. 

It was built in 2007 and features approximately 14,020 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 9 full and 3 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with staircase, elevator, formal living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, office, rear staircase, great room with wet bar, 7-car garage (3 attached /4 detached) garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, balcony, patio, kitchen/BBQ and a swimming pool.

🌍 263 Mount Laurel Road, Mount Laurel, New Jersey 🏠 14,020 Square Feet 🛏 7 Bedrooms 🛁 12 Bathrooms 💰 $5,000,000

Good morning! 😍 This stone & brick home is located at 2836 S 2300 E in Saint George, Utah and is situated on 3 acres of land.

It was built in 2018 and features over 17,000 square feet of living space with 8 bedrooms, 6 full and 5 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with staircase & elevator, dining room, gourmet kitchen, 2-story family room, office, home theater, gym, indoor spa with steam shower & sauna, indoor rock climbing wall, indoor foam pit with slide, 11-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a courtyard and terraces.

🌍 2836 S 2300 E, Saint George, Utah 🏠 17,000+ Square Feet 🛏 8 Bedrooms 🛁 11 Bathrooms 💰 $5,900,000

It was originally built in 1901 and has been completely renovated & expanded. It features approximately 13,000 square feet of living space with 5 bedrooms, 7 full and 2 half bathrooms, foyer with staircase, elevator, forma living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, paneled office, indoor half-court basketball court, wine cellar, enclosed porch with BBQ, 4-car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a covered 
front porch, decks, fireplace and an infinity pool with spa.

🌍 72 Miller Road, Morristown, New Jersey 🏠 13,000 Square Feet 🛏 5 Bedrooms 🛁 9 Bathrooms 💰 $5,900,000
